<% layout('boilerplate') %>

<head>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/categories.css">
</head>

<body>

  <div id="temp">
    <img src="/images/historic_banner.jpeg" alt="">
  </div>

  <div class="categories-div">
    <h1 class="categories-h1">Historic Places</h1>
    <p class="categories-p">
      India is a treasure trove of cultural and historical marvels, with iconic landmarks that showcase the
      nation's rich heritage. The Sun Temple in Gujarat, a stunning testament to intricate architecture, stands as
      a symbol of devotion and artistic excellence. The Hawa Mahal in Jaipur, with its unique honeycomb fa√ßade,
      beckons visitors to explore the royal history of Rajasthan. Moving north, the majestic Red Fort in Delhi, a
      UNESCO World Heritage site, encapsulates the grandeur of Mughal architecture and serves as a poignant
      reminder of India's struggle for independence. Further west, the Aguada Fort in Goa, perched on the shores
      of the Arabian Sea, narrates tales of Portuguese colonial rule and maritime history. Meanwhile, the City
      Palace in Udaipur, surrounded by the picturesque Lake Pichola, showcases the opulence and elegance of Rajput
      rulers. Concluding the journey in the capital, the India Gate stands proudly as a war memorial, honoring the
      sacrifices of Indian soldiers. Each of these landmarks contributes to India's diverse and vibrant tourism
      landscape, attracting visitors with their unique stories and architectural brilliance.
    </p>
  </div>

  <% if (places.length > 0) { %>
    <% places.forEach((place, index) => { %>
      <% if (index % 2 === 0) { %> <!-- Start a new row every 2 items -->
        <div class="o-div row">
      <% } %>

      <div class="d1 col-md-6">
        <img src="<%= place.category_page_image %>" alt="<%= place.name %>" class="mx-auto d-flex"
          onclick="openPage('/places/<%= place.slug %>')">
        <div class="title"><%= place.name %></div>
      </div>

      <% if (index % 2 === 1 || index === places.length - 1) { %> <!-- Close the row after 2 items or last item -->
        </div>
      <% } %>
    <% }) %>
  <% } %>
  
</body>